🚀 1. AI-Based Job Risk Predictor
🎯 Objective

To predict the probability of unemployment risk for a user using machine learning.

⚙️ Working
Input:
Skills
Education
Experience
Location (optional)
Processing:
Feature Engineering:
Skill demand score
Industry growth
ML Model:
Logistic Regression / Decision Tree
Output:
Risk Level (High/Medium/Low)
Probability %
Reason + Suggestions
🧠 Technology Stack
Python
Pandas, NumPy
Scikit-learn
(Optional) XGBoost
Streamlit / Flask (UI)
🔥 Advanced Add-on
“What-if analysis” (simulate skill improvement)
